3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible sub-category as GANs are a popular technique in the field of AI for generating synthetic data. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible sub-category as the paper deals with image synthesis and generation. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible sub-category as the paper discusses the use of GANs for image-to-video applications.
